<title>CANADA: CBRS reaffirms Hudson's Bay ratings.</title>
<headline>CBRS reaffirms Hudson's Bay ratings.</headline>
<dateline>MONTREAL 1997-05-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Canadian Bond Rating Service said on Tuesday it reaffirmed the ratings of Hudson's Bay Co's unsecured debentures at B++(High), secured debentures at A and its commercial paper at A-1(Low), with a stable outlook.</p>
<p>CBRS said HBC's capital structure remains stable and debt has been reduced.</p>
<p>&quot;Although cash flow from operations and operating income have improved, the company faces challenges to maintain market share and to maintain positive same store sales,&quot; CBRS said.</p>
<p>((Reuters Toronto Bureau (416) 941-8100))</p>
